elements.name: Create new post and publish it

steps.name: I enter "<EMAIL>" into input field having id "ember8"
I enter "<PASSWORD>" into input field having id "ember10"
I click on element having id "ember12"
I click on element having css selector "li.gh-nav-list-new a.gh-nav-new-post"
I enter "Create new post from Kraken title" into input field having css selector ".gh-editor-title"
I enter "Create new post from Kraken description" into input field having css selector "div.koenig-editor__editor.__mobiledoc-editor"
I click on element having css selector "div.gh-publishmenu > div.gh-publishmenu-trigger"
I click on element having css selector "button.gh-publishmenu-button"
